at it's designed to do.", "tokens": [50632, 400, 641, 11185, 307, 516, 281, 360, 2293, 437, 309, 311, 4761, 281, 360, 13, 50786], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1440225499016898, "compression_ratio": 1.9641255605381165, "no_speech_prob": 0.01594916544854641}, {"id": 46, "seek": 13752, "start": 145.96, "end": 150.96, "text": " Their browser is going to parse the HTML page, it's going to come across the JavaScript,", "tokens": [50786, 6710, 11185, 307, 516, 281, 48377, 264, 17995, 3028, 11, 309, 311, 516, 281, 808, 2108, 264, 15778, 11, 51036], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1440225499016898, "compression_ratio": 1.9641255605381165, "no_speech_prob": 0.01594916544854641}, {"id": 47, "seek": 13752, "start": 150.96, "end": 156.16000000000003, "text": " and it's going to execute the JavaScript, it's what it's designed to do.", "tokens": [51036, 293, 309, 311, 516, 281, 14483, 264, 15778, 11, 309, 311, 437, 309, 311, 4761, 281, 360, 13, 51296], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1440225499016898, "compression_ratio": 1.9641255605381165, "no_speech_prob": 0.01594916544854641}, {"id": 48, "seek": 13752, "start": 156.16000000000003, "end": 161.52, "text": " And now when our victim's browser executes that JavaScript code, what typically happens?", "tokens": [51296, 400, 586, 562, 527, 6760, 311, 11185, 4454, 1819, 300, 15778, 3089, 11, 437, 5850, 2314, 30, 51564], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1440225499016898, "compression_ratio": 1.9641255605381165, "no_speech_prob": 0.01594916544854641}, {"id": 49, "seek": 13752, "start": 161.52, "end": 165.92000000000002, "text": " Well, some data is sent back to our baddie here.", "tokens": [51564, 1042, 11, 512, 1412, 307, 2279, 646, 281, 527, 1578, 11231, 510, 13, 51784], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1440225499016898, "compression_ratio": 1.9641255605381165, "no_speech_prob": 0.01594916544854641}, {"id": 50, "seek": 16592, "start": 165.92, "end": 169.35999999999999, "text": " So this is an example of stored cross-site scripting.", "tokens": [50364, 407, 341, 307, 364, 1365, 295, 12187, 3278, 12, 30417, 5755, 278, 13, 50536], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14788006954505795, "compression_ratio": 1.833976833976834, "no_speech_prob": 0.0017873080214485526}, {"id": 51, "seek": 16592, "start": 169.35999999999999, "end": 170.72, "text": " Why do we call it stored?", "tokens": [50536, 1545, 360, 321, 818, 309, 12187, 30, 50604], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14788006954505795, "compression_ratio": 1.833976833976834, "no_speech_prob": 0.0017873080214485526}, {"id": 52, "seek": 16592, "start": 170.72, "end": 175.51999999999998, "text": " Well, it's because the JavaScript code is stored on the server.", "tokens": [50604, 1042, 11, 309, 311, 570, 264, 15778, 3089, 307, 12187, 322, 264, 7154, 13, 50844], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14788006954505795, "compression_ratio": 1.833976833976834, "no_speech_prob": 0.0017873080214485526}, {"id": 53, "seek": 16592, "start": 175.51999999999998, "end": 180.39999999999998, "text": " We also call it persistent, and the reason we call it persistent is because every subsequent", "tokens": [50844, 492, 611, 818, 309, 24315, 11, 293, 264, 1778, 321, 818, 309, 24315, 307, 570, 633, 19962, 51088], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14788006954505795, "compression_ratio": 1.833976833976834, "no_speech_prob": 0.0017873080214485526}, {"id": 54, "seek": 16592, "start": 180.39999999999998, "end": 185.11999999999998, "text": " user that goes to this particular page and views, you know, and downloads this malicious", "tokens": [51088, 4195, 300, 1709, 281, 341, 1729, 3028, 293, 6809, 11, 291, 458, 11, 293, 36553, 341, 33496, 51324], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14788006954505795, "compression_ratio": 1.833976833976834, "no_speech_prob": 0.0017873080214485526}, {"id": 55, "seek": 16592, "start": 185.11999999999998, "end": 188.07999999999998, "text": " code, it's going to execute on their browser.", "tokens": [51324, 3089, 11, 309, 311, 516, 281, 14483, 322, 641, 11185, 13, 51472], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14788006954505795, "compression_ratio": 1.833976833976834, "no_speech_prob": 0.0017873080214485526}, {"id": 56, "seek": 16592, "start": 188.07999999999998, "end": 192.39999999999998, "text": " So stored, persistent, cross-site scripting.", "tokens": [51472, 407, 12187, 11, 24315, 11, 3278, 12, 30417, 5755, 278, 13, 51688], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14788006954505795, "compression_ratio": 1.833976833976834, "no_speech_prob": 0.0017873080214485526}, {"id": 57, "seek": 16592, "start": 192.39999999999998, "end": 195.32, "text": " Now let's talk about another type of cross-site scripting.", "tokens": [51688, 823, 718, 311, 751, 466, 1071, 2010, 295, 3278, 12, 30417, 5755, 278, 13, 51834], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14788006954505795, "compression_ratio": 1.833976833976834, "no_speech_prob": 0.0017873080214485526}, {"id": 58, "seek": 19532, "start": 195.32, "end": 198.35999999999999, "text": " This is known as reflected cross-site scripting.", "tokens": [50364, 639, 307, 2570, 382, 15502, 3278, 12, 30417, 5755, 278, 13, 50516], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17390392062900303, "compression_ratio": 1.7231404958677685, "no_speech_prob": 0.003118684282526374}, {"id": 59, "seek": 19532, "start": 198.35999999999999, "end": 203.35999999999999, "text": " So I'm going to set up another little scenario to help you imagine how this works.", "tokens": [50516, 407, 286, 478, 516, 281, 992, 493, 1071, 707, 9005, 281, 854, 291, 3811, 577, 341, 1985, 13, 50766], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17390392062900303, "compression_ratio": 1.7231404958677685, "no_speech_prob": 0.003118684282526374}, {"id": 60, "seek": 19532, "start": 203.35999999999999, "end": 206.4, "text": " Imagine going to a website like Google.com.", "tokens": [50766, 11739, 516, 281, 257, 3144, 411, 3329, 13, 1112, 13, 50918], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17390392062900303, "compression_ratio": 1.7231404958677685, "no_speech_prob": 0.003118684282526374}, {"id": 61, "seek": 19532, "start": 206.4, "end": 211.32, "text": " When you go to Google, when you go to Google.com, and you type in a search query in the search", "tokens": [50918, 1133, 291, 352, 281, 3329, 11, 562, 291, 352, 281, 3329, 13, 1112, 11, 293, 291, 2010, 294, 257, 3164, 14581, 294, 264, 3164, 51164], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17390392062900303, "compression_ratio": 1.7231404958677685, "no_speech_prob": 0.003118684282526374}, {"id": 62, "seek": 19532, "start": 211.32, "end": 214.4, "text": " bar and hit search, what happens?", "tokens": [51164, 2159, 293, 2045, 3164, 11, 437, 2314, 30, 51318], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17390392062900303, "compression_ratio": 1.7231404958677685, "no_speech_prob": 0.003118684282526374}, {"id": 63, "seek": 19532, "start": 214.4, "end": 220.04, "text": " Well, the search results page says, here are your search results for cat or dog or whatever", "tokens": [51318, 1042, 11, 264, 3164, 3542, 3028, 1619, 11, 510, 366, 428, 3164, 3542, 337, 3857, 420, 3000, 420, 2035, 51600], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17390392062900303, "compression_ratio": 1.7231404958677685, "no_speech_prob": 0.003118684282526374}, {"id": 64, "seek": 19532, "start": 220.04, "end": 223.0, "text": " you've searched for.", "tokens": [51600, 291, 600, 22961, 337, 13, 51748], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17390392062900303, "compression_ratio": 1.7231404958677685, "no_speech_prob": 0.003118684282526374}, {"id": 65, "seek": 22300, "start": 223.0, "end": 225.68, "text": " So imagine that scenario, OK?", "tokens": [50364, 407, 3811, 300, 9005, 11, 2264, 30, 50498], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16161547285137753, "compression_ratio": 1.7732342007434945, "no_speech_prob": 0.0030837568920105696}, {"id": 66, "seek": 22300, "start": 225.68, "end": 226.76, "text": " So here's what's going to happen.", "tokens": [50498, 407, 510, 311, 437, 311, 516, 281, 1051, 13, 50552], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16161547285137753, "compression_ratio": 1.7732342007434945, "no_speech_prob": 0.0030837568920105696}, {"id": 67, "seek": 22300, "start": 226.76, "end": 230.36, "text": " Our baddie is going to do, again, discover a vulnerable website.", "tokens": [50552, 2621, 1578, 11231, 307, 516, 281, 360, 11, 797, 11, 4411, 257, 10955, 3144, 13, 50732], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16161547285137753, "compression_ratio": 1.7732342007434945, "no_speech_prob": 0.0030837568920105696}, {"id": 68, "seek": 22300, "start": 230.36, "end": 234.04, "text": " And our baddie is going to first create a URL.", "tokens": [50732, 400, 527, 1578, 11231, 307, 516, 281, 700, 1884, 257, 12905, 13, 50916], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16161547285137753, "compression_ratio": 1.7732342007434945, "no_speech_prob": 0.0030837568920105696}, {"id": 69, "seek": 22300, "start": 234.04, "end": 236.64, "text": " A URL stands for a universal resource locator.", "tokens": [50916, 316, 12905, 7382, 337, 257, 11455, 7684, 1628, 1639, 13, 51046], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16161547285137753, "compression_ratio": 1.7732342007434945, "no_speech_prob": 0.0030837568920105696}, {"id": 70, "seek": 22300, "start": 236.64, "end": 240.68, "text": " This is what you type up in your browser bar to go to a particular site or page on a", "tokens": [51046, 639, 307, 437, 291, 2010, 493, 294, 428, 11185, 2159, 281, 352, 281, 257, 1729, 3621, 420, 3028, 322, 257, 51248], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16161547285137753, "compression_ratio": 1.7732342007434945, "no_speech_prob": 0.0030837568920105696}, {"id": 71, "seek": 22300, "start": 240.68, "end": 242.16, "text": " website.", "tokens": [51248, 3144, 13, 51322], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16161547285137753, "compression_ratio": 1.7732342007434945, "no_speech_prob": 0.0030837568920105696}, {"id": 72, "seek": 22300, "start": 242.16, "end": 245.88, "text": " And what our baddie is going to do here is think of Google.com again.", "tokens": [51322, 400, 437, 527, 1578, 11231, 307, 516, 281, 360, 510, 307, 519, 295, 3329, 13, 1112, 797, 13, 51508], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16161547285137753, "compression_ratio": 1.7732342007434945, "no_speech_prob": 0.0030837568920105696}, {"id": 73, "seek": 22300, "start": 245.88, "end": 250.72, "text": " When you type in Google.com and you search for something, the search results URL page will", "tokens": [51508, 1133, 291, 2010, 294, 3329, 13, 1112, 293, 291, 3164, 337, 746, 11, 264, 3164, 3542, 12905, 3028, 486, 51750], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16161547285137753, "compression_ratio": 1.7732342007434945, "no_speech_prob": 0.0030837568920105696}, {"id": 74, "seek": 25072, "start": 250.72, "end": 257.6, "text": " say Google.com, question mark, search equals, whatever you searched for.", "tokens": [50364, 584, 3329, 13, 1112, 11, 1168, 1491, 11, 3164, 6915, 11, 2035, 291, 22961, 337, 13, 50708], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17157181273115443, "compression_ratio": 1.6342592592592593, "no_speech_prob": 0.0037690226454287767}, {"id": 75, "seek": 25072, "start": 257.6, "end": 261.72, "text": " Our baddie is going to create a URL for like that, except in the search field, instead of", "tokens": [50708, 2621, 1578, 11231, 307, 516, 281, 1884, 257, 12905, 337, 411, 300, 11, 3993, 294, 264, 3164, 2519, 11, 2602, 295, 50914], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17157181273115443, "compression_ratio": 1.6342592592592593, "no_speech_prob": 0.0037690226454287767}, {"id": 76, "seek": 25072, "start": 261.72, "end": 267.12, "text": " putting in some word or some sentence, what's our baddie going to put in the URL?", "tokens": [50914, 3372, 294, 512, 1349, 420, 512, 8174, 11, 437, 311, 527, 1578, 11231, 516, 281, 829, 294, 264, 12905, 30, 51184], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17157181273115443, "compression_ratio": 1.6342592592592593, "no_speech_prob": 0.0037690226454287767}, {"id": 77, "seek": 25072, "start": 267.12, "end": 268.76, "text": " JavaScript code.", "tokens": [51184, 15778, 3089, 13, 51266], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17157181273115443, "compression_ratio": 1.6342592592592593, "no_speech_prob": 0.0037690226454287767}, {"id": 78, "seek": 25072, "start": 268.76, "end": 273.24, "text": " So our baddie creates this URL containing the JavaScript code.", "tokens": [51266, 407, 527, 1578, 11231, 7829, 341, 12905, 19273, 264, 15778, 3089, 13, 51490], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17157181273115443, "compression_ratio": 1.6342592592592593, "no_speech_prob": 0.0037690226454287767}, {"id": 79, "seek": 25072, "start": 273.24, "end": 276.36, "text": " Sends it to our victim here.", "tokens": [51490, 318, 2581, 309, 281, 527, 6760, 510, 13, 51646], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17157181273115443, "compression_ratio": 1.6342592592592593, "no_speech_prob": 0.0037690226454287767}, {"id": 80, "seek": 27636, "start": 276.36, "end": 280.92, "text": " And through some sort of social engineering technique, maybe phishing or something like", "tokens": [50364, 400, 807, 512, 1333, 295, 2093, 7043, 6532, 11, 1310, 903, 3807, 420, 746, 411, 50592], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12194916353387347, "compression_ratio": 1.8515625, "no_speech_prob": 0.13054020702838898}, {"id": 81, "seek": 27636, "start": 280.92, "end": 286.28000000000003, "text": " that, our baddie here somehow convinces the user to click on the URL.", "tokens": [50592, 300, 11, 527, 1578, 11231, 510, 6063, 9854, 887, 264, 4195, 281, 2052, 322, 264, 12905, 13, 50860], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12194916353387347, "compression_ratio": 1.8515625, "no_speech_prob": 0.13054020702838898}, {"id": 82, "seek": 27636, "start": 286.28000000000003, "end": 290.92, "text": " When the user clicks on the URL, that sends the request to the web server.", "tokens": [50860, 1133, 264, 4195, 18521, 322, 264, 12905, 11, 300, 14790, 264, 5308, 281, 264, 3670, 7154, 13, 51092], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12194916353387347, "compression_ratio": 1.8515625, "no_speech_prob": 0.13054020702838898}, {"id": 83, "seek": 27636, "start": 290.92, "end": 294.56, "text": " The web server is going to then reflect that code back to the user.", "tokens": [51092, 440, 3670, 7154, 307, 516, 281, 550, 5031, 300, 3089, 646, 281, 264, 4195, 13, 51274], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12194916353387347, "compression_ratio": 1.8515625, "no_speech_prob": 0.13054020702838898}, {"id": 84, "seek": 27636, "start": 294.56, "end": 295.56, "text": " It's like the search.", "tokens": [51274, 467, 311, 411, 264, 3164, 13, 51324], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12194916353387347, "compression_ratio": 1.8515625, "no_speech_prob": 0.13054020702838898}, {"id": 85, "seek": 27636, "start": 295.56, "end": 299.68, "text": " It's like the page is saying, here are your search results for JavaScript code.", "tokens": [51324, 467, 311, 411, 264, 3028, 307, 1566, 11, 510, 366, 428, 3164, 3542, 337, 15778, 3089, 13, 51530], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12194916353387347, "compression_ratio": 1.8515625, "no_speech_prob": 0.13054020702838898}, {"id": 86, "seek": 27636, "start": 299.68, "end": 304.64, "text": " So the website is going to reflect the malicious code back to the user.", "tokens": [51530, 407, 264, 3144, 307, 516, 281, 5031, 264, 33496, 3089, 646, 281, 264, 4195, 13, 51778], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12194916353387347, "compression_ratio": 1.8515625, "no_speech_prob": 0.13054020702838898}, {"id": 87, "seek": 30464, "start": 304.64, "end": 309.8, "text": " The malicious code is going to be contained in the page that comes back to the user.", "tokens": [50364, 440, 33496, 3089, 307, 516, 281, 312, 16212, 294, 264, 3028, 300, 1487, 646, 281, 264, 4195, 13, 50622], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1290383259455363, "compression_ratio": 1.8605577689243027, "no_speech_prob": 0.001733603305183351}, {"id": 88, "seek": 30464, "start": 309.8, "end": 313.08, "text": " And once our users browse are going to do, exactly what it's designed to do.", "tokens": [50622, 400, 1564, 527, 5022, 31442, 366, 516, 281, 360, 11, 2293, 437, 309, 311, 4761, 281, 360, 13, 50786], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1290383259455363, "compression_ratio": 1.8605577689243027, "no_speech_prob": 0.001733603305183351}, {"id": 89, "seek": 30464, "start": 313.08, "end": 319.15999999999997, "text": " It's going to parse through the page, hit the malicious JavaScript code and execute it.", "tokens": [50786, 467, 311, 516, 281, 48377, 807, 264, 3028, 11, 2045, 264, 33496, 15778, 3089, 293, 14483, 309, 13, 51090], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1290383259455363, "compression_ratio": 1.8605577689243027, "no_speech_prob": 0.001733603305183351}, {"id": 90, "seek": 30464, "start": 319.15999999999997, "end": 326.4, "text": " And once the final step here, well, this malicious code is going to run and it's going to send", "tokens": [51090, 400, 1564, 264, 2572, 1823, 510, 11, 731, 11, 341, 33496, 3089, 307, 516, 281, 1190, 293, 309, 311, 516, 281, 2845, 51452], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1290383259455363, "compression_ratio": 1.8605577689243027, "no_speech_prob": 0.001733603305183351}, {"id": 91, "seek": 30464, "start": 326.4, "end": 329.24, "text": " some data back to the baddie once again.", "tokens": [51452, 512, 1412, 646, 281, 264, 1578, 11231, 1564, 797, 13, 51594], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1290383259455363, "compression_ratio": 1.8605577689243027, "no_speech_prob": 0.001733603305183351}, {"id": 92, "seek": 30464, "start": 329.24, "end": 334.4, "text": " So overall, it's the same effect, which is the target of attack here is the user.", "tokens": [51594, 407, 4787, 11, 309, 311, 264, 912, 1802, 11, 597, 307, 264, 3779, 295, 2690, 510, 307, 264, 4195, 13, 51852], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1290383259455363, "compression_ratio": 1.8605577689243027, "no_speech_pr